thread.title: Salukis dominant in road win at Missouri State

author: TIM MCCAUGHAN For The Southern
title: Salukis dominant in road win at Missouri State
text:
SPRINGFIELD, MO. â€” Southern Illinois University Men's Basketball swept the season series against Missouri State after securing a 73-51 win Wednesday night at Great Southern Bank Arena.
The Salukis led wire-to-wire and put up their second-best defensive game of the season behind holding North Dakota State to 44 at home in November.
